    <h2 class="marginZero padding15">Quality Control Services</h2>
    <p>Today, effective quality control mechanisms remain a priority for any business looking to secure their supply chain.</p>
    <p>With a global coverage of 85 countries, AI performs <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/pre-shipment-inspection">product inspections</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/quality-control-services/laboratory-testing">lab testing</a> and <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/manufacturing-audit">supplier audits</a>, helping you ensure product quality, avoid supply chain disruptions and protect your brand reputation by being <b>Your Eyes in the Factory! &trade;</b></p>

    <h2 class="marginZero padding15">Supplier Audits</h2>
    <p>AI's highly qualified auditors can conduct <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/manufacturing-audit">Manufacturing</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/ethical-audit">Ethical</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/structural-audits">Structural</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/environmental-audit">Environmental</a> and <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/c-tpat-compliance">C-TPAT</a> audits of your suppliers' factories, helping you engage with capable and ethical factories. AI Auditors will assess and investigate your suppliers’ manufacturing means, working conditions, environmental and ecological impact. AI conducts audits to a number of international standards, our own Best-in-Class protocol or your in-house requirements. </p>
    <p>AI Supplier Audits help you:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left:15px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom:5px">Protect your brand against operational and ethical risks</li>
