    <p>AI operates in house testing labs which are fully accredited to perform a wide range of tests on products. AI labs offer over 6,000 tests in a number of categories, including <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/industry-softline">softlines</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/industry-hardline">hardlines</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/testing/eyewear">eyewear</a>, promotional items, textiles, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/testing/garments-apparel">apparel</a>, <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/testing/toy-safety-and-lab-testing">toys and children's products</a>, and more.</p>
    <p>Our lab testing capabilities are accredited by and in accordance with the following regulatory bodies and international standards:</p>
